<title>
P/S Motor Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hoist vehicle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using ammeter (3), check that P/S motor current with engine idling is as indicated below. If check result is not as specified, check P/S control module. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A6304022"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is as specified, replace steering column assembly.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Motor current at hoisted vehicle
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1" page = "2">
